name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Google Meet Attendance: Participants to CSV

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Save the names of your Google Meet participants to a CSV file instantly... Works perfectly with the new Google Meet UI

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
An easy to use extension for instantly saving the names of your meeting participants to a CSV file. 
It doesn't change your meet window in any way so it assures you an uninterrupted meeting while the extension can be used anytime.

WORKS WITH THE NEW GOOGLE MEET INTERFACE
